34#ifndef _IPSEC_STRERROR_H
35#define _IPSEC_STRERROR_H
36
37extern int __ipsec_errcode;
38extern void __ipsec_set_strerror(const char *);
39
40#define EIPSEC_NO_ERROR 0 /*success*/
41#define EIPSEC_NOT_SUPPORTED 1 /*not supported*/
42#define EIPSEC_INVAL_ARGUMENT 2 /*invalid argument*/
43#define EIPSEC_INVAL_SADBMSG 3 /*invalid sadb message*/
44#define EIPSEC_INVAL_VERSION 4 /*invalid version*/
45#define EIPSEC_INVAL_POLICY 5 /*invalid security policy*/
46#define EIPSEC_INVAL_ADDRESS 6 /*invalid address specification*/
47#define EIPSEC_INVAL_PROTO 7 /*invalid ipsec protocol*/
48#define EIPSEC_INVAL_MODE 8 /*Invalid ipsec mode*/
49#define EIPSEC_INVAL_LEVEL 9 /*invalid ipsec level*/
50#define EIPSEC_INVAL_SATYPE 10 /*invalid SA type*/
51#define EIPSEC_INVAL_MSGTYPE 11 /*invalid message type*/
52#define EIPSEC_INVAL_EXTTYPE 12 /*invalid extension type*/
53#define EIPSEC_INVAL_ALGS 13 /*Invalid algorithm type*/
54#define EIPSEC_INVAL_KEYLEN 14 /*invalid key length*/
55#define EIPSEC_INVAL_FAMILY 15 /*invalid address family*/
56#define EIPSEC_INVAL_PREFIXLEN 16 /*SPI range violation*/
57#define EIPSEC_INVAL_DIR 17 /*Invalid direciton*/
58#define EIPSEC_INVAL_SPI 18 /*invalid prefixlen*/
59#define EIPSEC_NO_PROTO 19 /*no protocol specified*/
60#define EIPSEC_NO_ALGS 20 /*No algorithm specified*/
61#define EIPSEC_NO_BUFS 21 /*no buffers available*/
62#define EIPSEC_DO_GET_SUPP_LIST 22 /*must get supported algorithm first*/
63#define EIPSEC_PROTO_MISMATCH 23 /*protocol mismatch*/
64#define EIPSEC_FAMILY_MISMATCH 24 /*family mismatch*/
65#define EIPSEC_FEW_ARGUMENTS 25 /*Too few arguments*/
66#define EIPSEC_SYSTEM_ERROR 26 /*system error*/
67#define EIPSEC_INVAL_PRIORITY_OFFSET 27 /*priority offset out of range*/
68#define EIPSEC_INVAL_PRIORITY_BASE_OFFSET 28 /* priority base offset too
69 large */
70#define EIPSEC_PRIORITY_NOT_COMPILED 29 /*no priority support in libipsec*/
71#define EIPSEC_MAX 30 /*unknown error*/
72
73#endif /* _IPSEC_STRERROR_H */
